Class KeyRequestData

java.lang.Object
  com.netflix.msl.keyx.KeyRequestData
Direct Known Subclasses:
AsymmetricWrappedExchange.RequestData, DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData, JsonWebEncryptionLadderExchange.RequestData, JsonWebKeyLadderExchange.RequestData, SymmetricWrappedExchange.RequestData
public abstract class KeyRequestData
extends Object

Key request data contains all the data needed to facilitate a exchange of session keys with the requesting entity.

Specific key exchange mechanisms should define their own key request data types.

Key request data is represented as keyrequestdata = { "#mandatory" : [ "scheme", "keydata" ], "scheme" : "string", "keydata" : object } where:

  • scheme is the key exchange scheme
  • keydata is the scheme-specific key data
